(40, 23, 9, 62, 3, 1, 1, 'your Father, which is in heaven', 'Fatherhood of God', 'This connection highlights the concept of God as the Father. Both passages emphasize the relationship between believers and God, identifying Him as the ultimate Father.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
